summary: A set of presets for RaceMenu 3
descriptionHtml:
These are .jslot preset files for RaceMenu 3

[b]Installation:[/b]

Place file in Skyrim -> Data -> SKSE -> Plugins -> CharGen -> Presets

[b]How to use:[/b]

1) Select Nord as race
2) Go to the preset tab and load preset (F9 usually)

If you are using this on an old character type showracemenu in the console and follow the steps mentioned above

Body mod used in the pictures: [url=http://www.ladymoiraine.com/forum/index.php?topic=8263.0]SAM[/url]
